Wathoni, one of the ex-Housemate of the 2020 BBNaija reality show Lockdown edition, has revealed the most hurtful thing she heard about her from a fellow ex-housemate. “Erica said men who came after me were tasteless and that really hurt me,” Wathoni told Ebuka at the Tuesday night, June 29, 2021, episode of the BBNaija Reunion show. The mother of one made the revelation to viewers and fans when the show host, Ebuka Obi-Uchendu, asked the most hurtful thing she heard about her from a housemate after the show. In the previous episode, Wathoni and Erica settled their differences and hugged one another.without caution. They also admittedly settled the perceived biff with each other and decided to remain friends.